<div class="card">
  <h3>Victory Conditions</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Victory Points:</strong> First to 30 VP wins immediately</li>
    <li><strong>Dominance:</strong> Play a dominance card to change your win condition to controlling specific clearings</li>
    <li><strong>Coalition:</strong> The Wanderer may form a coalition with another player to share victory</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h3>Cards &amp; Crafting</h3>
  <p>
    The shared deck contains Ambush cards (for combat), Item cards (for crafting), and special Favor cards 
    (powerful effects). To craft an item, you must rule clearings matching the card's crafting cost. 
    Crafted items score victory points or give you powerful abilities.
  </p>
</div>
